<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Web Development Boot Camp</title>

<style>

*{
margin:0;
padding:0;
box-sizing:border-box;
font-family:Arial, sans-serif;
}

body{
line-height:1.6;
background:#f8f9fa;
}

/* Header */

header{
background:linear-gradient(90deg,#ff6b6b,#ff3b3b);
color:white;
padding:30px 10px;
text-align:center;
}

header h1{
font-size:34px;
}

header h2{
margin-top:5px;
}

header p{
margin-top:10px;
}

/* Hero Section */

.hero{
background:white;
padding:70px 20px;
text-align:center;
}

.hero h2{
font-size:32px;
margin-bottom:20px;
}

.hero p{
max-width:650px;
margin:auto;
margin-bottom:25px;
font-size:17px;
}

/* Button */

.btn{
display:inline-block;
background:#ff6b6b;
color:white;
padding:12px 28px;
border-radius:6px;
text-decoration:none;
font-weight:bold;
transition:0.3s;
}

.btn:hover{
background:#ff3b3b;
transform:scale(1.05);
}

/* Features */

.features{
display:flex;
flex-wrap:wrap;
justify-content:center;
gap:25px;
padding:50px 20px;
background:#ffffff;
}

.feature-box{
background:#f9f9f9;
padding:30px;
width:280px;
border-radius:10px;
text-align:center;
box-shadow:0 5px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
transition:0.3s;
}

.feature-box:hover{
transform:translateY(-8px);
box-shadow:0 10px 25px rgba(0,0,0,0.2);
}

.feature-box h3{
margin-bottom:10px;
color:#ff6b6b;
}

/* Instructor */

.instructor{
background:#eef2f7;
padding:50px 20px;
text-align:center;
}

.instructor img{
width:120px;
border-radius:50%;
margin:15px 0;
border:4px solid #ff6b6b;
}

/* Footer */

footer{
background:#222;
color:white;
text-align:center;
padding:20px;
margin-top:20px;
}

/* Responsive */

@media(max-width:768px){

.hero h2{
font-size:26px;
}

header h1{
font-size:26px;
}

.features{
flex-direction:column;
align-items:center;
}

}

</style>
</head>

<body>

<header>
<h1>SYMBIOSIS INSTITUTE OF TECHNOLOGY, NAGPUR</h1>
<h2>Web Development Boot Camp</h2>
<p>Learn HTML, CSS, JavaScript and build real projects</p>
</header>

<section class="hero">
<h2>Become a Web Developer in 8 Weeks</h2>
<p>Join our intensive boot camp designed for beginners and aspiring developers. Learn modern web development and build your own websites.</p>
<a href="#" class="btn">Enroll Now</a>
</section>

<section class="features">

<div class="feature-box">
<h3> Hands-on Projects</h3>
<p>Build real-world websites and applications during the boot camp.</p>
</div>

<div class="feature-box">
<h3> Expert Mentors</h3>
<p>Learn from experienced web developers and industry professionals.</p>
</div>

<div class="feature-box">
<h3> Certification</h3>
<p>Receive a certificate after completing the boot camp successfully.</p>
</div>

</section>

<section class="instructor">

<h2>Meet Your Instructor</h2>
<p><b>RASHI BANGRE</b> – Senior Web Developer with 1+ years experience teaching web technologies.</p>

</section>

<footer>

<p>© 2026 Web Development Boot Camp | Contact: info@bootcamp.com</p>

</footer>

</body>
</html>
